x-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心调整点：</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">为便于商家区分违规场景，避免与&rdquo;发布混淆信息&ldquo;违规场景混淆，</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">将【品牌词混淆】表述更改为【品牌信息不一致】。</span></span></p>",
